<li><a href="http://txpq.com/" class="external text" title="http://txpq.com/" rel="nofollow">TXPQ Magazine</a>: Articles and interviews relating to Textpattern.</li>
<li><a href="http://welovetxp.com/" class="external text" title="http://welovetxp.com/" rel="nofollow">We Love Txp</a>: Showcase website built with Textpattern.</li>
<li><a href="http://txplanet.net/" class="external text" title="http://txplanet.net/" rel="nofollow">Textpattern Planet</a>: Textpattern news aggregator.</li>
<li><a href="http://textpattern.ivorius.com/" class="external text" title="http://textpattern.ivorius.com/" rel="nofollow">Textpattern Czech</a>: Czech language Textpattern information site.</li>
<li><a href="http://textpattern.ru/" class="external text" title="http://textpattern.ru/" rel="nofollow">Textpattern Russian</a>: Russian language Textpattern information site.</li>
